 None ng-touched\" spellcheck=\"false\"><b>Key points covered in this module are:</b><div><b><br></b><div>Performance management is a process that contributes to the effective management of individuals and teams in order to achieve the goals of an organization.</div></div></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"a467T\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed selected-class   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty text-left None ng-touched background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" spellcheck=\"false\"><h6 class=\"background\">Importance of Performance Management</h6></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"ZSfPi\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed   ui-resizable border\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched\" spellcheck=\"false\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">It regularly provides open and transparent feedback to the employees to help them improve their performance.</li><li class=\"\">Performance reviews provide an opportunity for clarifying expectations and open communication.</li><li class=\"\">It establishes a clear linkage between performance and compensation</li><li class=\"\">It recognizes and rewards good performance in an organization by distributing incentives and rewards on a fair and transparent basis</li><li class=\"\">It provides the opportunity for discussing the development opportunities and career aspirations leading to employee development.</li><li class=\"\">It provides maximum opportunities for career growth based on performance.</li><li class=\"\">Employees are encouraged to improve their performance on a continuous basis</li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"